Description: Cylinder seal of black steatite: perforated through the centre, bearing an incised inscription. Surface rather worn.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit III (Wiesbaden, 1964), pl. 114, abb. 638; P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit II (Wiesbaden, 1964), 1173.
